<%- include('../partials/header', { title, currentUser }) %>

<section class="page-head split">
  <h1>Company Profile</h1>
  <a class="btn" href="/company-profile.pdf">Download Profile PDF</a>
</section>

<section class="profile-showcase card">
  <div class="profile-showcase-copy">
    <h3>At the Heart of the Chrome Corridor</h3>
    <p>
      From our Steelpoort base, Bilatechral Solutions supports the practical movement of chrome
      from stockpile to market with operating discipline, dependable handling and transparent
      weighbridge records.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="profile-showcase-image">
    <img
      src="/images/hero/hero-2-900.jpg"
      srcset="/images/hero/hero-2-900.jpg 900w, /images/hero/hero-2-1600.jpg 1600w"
      sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 48vw"
      alt="Bilatechral operations site"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h3>Who We Are</h3>
  <p>
    Bilatechral Solutions is positioned in Steelpoort as a practical exchange point for the
    chrome value chain. We support mines and traders with a dependable operating base where
    product can be received, stockpiled, tested and moved onward to market.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="cards two">
  <article class="card">
    <h3>Company Details</h3>
    <ul class="list">
      <li><strong>Name:</strong> Bilatechral Solutions (PTY) Ltd</li>
      <li><strong>Reg Nr:</strong> 2023/910602/07</li>
      <li><strong>Managing Director:</strong> Freddy Mkhabela</li>
      <li><strong>Address:</strong> Portion 5, Olifanstpoortje 319 KT, Extention 23, Steelpoort</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
  <article class="card">
    <h3>Nature of Business</h3>
    <ul class="list">
      <li>Chrome ore mining operations</li>
      <li>Stockpiling facilities for testing and onward sale</li>
      <li>On-site weighbridge support for transport requirements</li>
      <li>Chrome ROM and concentrate flow facilitation</li>
      <li>Service footprint: Steelpoort, Burgersfort and the Eastern Limpopo BIC</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="cards two">
  <article class="card">
    <h3>Commercial Role</h3>
    <p>
      In addition to operational handling, we maintain access to multiple offtake end-customers,
      helping mines and traders move product more efficiently from stockpile to sale.
    </p>
  </article>
  <article class="card">
    <h3>Customer Base</h3>
    <p>
      Our customer mix includes companies such as Global Nexus Trade, Umbono We Langa Mining,
      Energim, and other established mines and traders across the region.
    </p>
  </article>
</section>

